you told her to?

19:04.935 --> 19:06.478
She took direction well.

19:07.855 --> 19:11.108
You know,
I translated "The Maids."

19:11.191 --> 19:13.068
Of course I know.

19:13.151 --> 19:15.737
I used your translation.

19:15.821 --> 19:17.906
