Oh!

20:02.492 --> 20:03.785
James Beard here.

20:03.869 --> 20:06.496
I need to borrow your wife
for a while longer.

20:06.580 --> 20:09.583
We have an important mission
in the Mission.

20:11.293 --> 20:16.131
Join us if you can,
but there's no time to waste.

20:16.214 --> 20:18.050
Are you up for it?

20:18.133 --> 20:23.096
