I just love.

23:34.371 --> 23:35.872
I traded in my old wig.

23:35.956 --> 23:40.252
My Donna Reed days are over,
and Coco's here to stay.

23:40.335 --> 23:43.880
Now, I must say, Julia,
you are as pretty as a picture.

23:43.964 --> 23:46.383
Just like on TV.

23:46.466 --> 23:48.552
Your makeup is
beautifully done.

23:48.635 --> 23:51.346
The trick is the cheekbones.

23:51.429 --> 23:53.723
See, I made my face
like this...

23:53.807 --> 23:55.684
and then sweep up!

23:55.767 --> 23:57.644
Always up!
Always up!

23:57.727 --> 23:59.104
Makeup's
the fun part.

23:59.187 --> 24:01.356
The hard part
is the shoes.

24:01.439 --> 24:03.024
