at work.

31:12.036 --> 31:14.664
I have to constantly
explain myself,

31:14.747 --> 31:17.959
who I am,
why I'm there,

31:18.042 --> 31:19.502
and when I come to you,

31:19.586 --> 31:22.213
sometimes, I just want
you to listen.

31:22.297 --> 31:23.923
Oh.

31:24.007 --> 31:25.758
Alice.

31:25.842 --> 31:29.137
