a-a cookbook editor.

32:41.376 --> 32:43.836
Places, everyone.
One minute to go.

32:43.920 --> 32:46.422
We should find
our seats.

32:46.506 --> 32:49.384
Live audience members can
go ahead and take your seats.

32:49.467 --> 32:52.387
Let's move cameras to marks
and fly equipment out.

32:54.681 --> 32:57.642
This is a universal
crepe batter.

32:57.725 --> 33:02.939
You may add spices to the mix
if you like, or nutmeg.

33:03.022 --> 33:05.149
Good wrist work, Ken.

33:05.233 --> 33:07.235
I can see you've had
plenty of practice.

33:08.861 --> 33:11.948
Have you made crepes
like this before, Ken?

33:12.031 --> 33:14.575
Haven't used a hot plate
since chemistry class.

33:14.659 --> 33:16.994
Oh, well, cooking is just
like chemistry,

33:17.078 --> 33:20.832
but we are encouraged
to lick the instruments.

33:23.334 --> 33:26.045
