There you are.

34:51.672 --> 34:53.174
Oh!

34:53.257 --> 34:56.177
Teaching America how to cook
is hard work, I see.

34:56.260 --> 34:58.679
Those lights were
awfully hot.

34:58.763 --> 35:01.724
Anyway, I'd best be off.
I have a plane to catch.

35:01.808 --> 35:04.435
