awhile longer?

35:07.897 --> 35:09.315
No more play for me.

35:09.398 --> 35:12.068
Julialand is the most
entertaining place,

35:12.151 --> 35:14.695
but there is a mile-high
stack of novels

35:14.779 --> 35:17.198
in my office
calling me away.

35:17.281 --> 35:18.699
It's good.

35:18.783 --> 35:21.828
It's my work.

35:21.911 --> 35:26.374
